It has emerged that Deputy Finance Minister Mcebisi Jonas lied about being offered a Finance Minister’s job by the Guptas. This was revealed in a letter written by Jonas’ friend and business partner Fana Hlongwane. Hlongwane’s letter which is addressed to the Public Protector Thuli Madonsela was seen by The Citizen newspaper. The letter seeks to clarify reasons why Hlongwane and Jonas met with Gupta family member in Hyatt Hotel in Johannesburg. Here is the copy of Hlongwane’s letter:   (adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});





